You need to create an app on twitter. To do so, visit https://apps.twitter.com

Generate your own CONSUMER_KEY, CONSUMER_SECRET, ACCESS_KEY, ACCESS_SECRET and add them to the main-script file.

Similarily, generate your own openweathermap API key(https://http://openweathermap.org/api) and 
WAQI(http://aqicn.org/data-platform/token/#/) Token and add them in the 'url'and 'poll_url' line. 
